quran[135]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,"Tɑɑhɑɑ."
  20,2,"Tõnd pa sik AlKʋrãanã fo zug tɩ yɩ sɑbɑb tɩ fo nams ye."
  20,3,"A pa bũmb a to rẽnda tẽegr ne ned ning sẽn yaeesd Wẽnde."
  20,4,"A sigame n yi sẽn naan-a tẽngã la sasã sẽn zẽkã nengẽ."
  20,5,"Yolsg Naabã, A zẽkɑ Naamã goeel yĩngri (zẽkr sẽn sõm ne Wende)."
  20,6,"Yẽnd n so bũmb ning sẽn be sãasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã la sẽn be b yiibã sʋka la sẽn be tomã tẽngrã."
  20,7,"Fo sã n zẽk f koεεga, mɑɑ f solg-ɑ lame, ad A mii sẽn solg la sẽn tʋg n solg n yɩɩda."
  20,8,"Wẽnde, Soab ka be rẽnda Yẽnda, yʋ-yɩlems yaa Yẽnd n so."
  20,9,"Lɑ rẽ yĩnga a Muusã kɩbarã waa fo nengẽ?"
  20,10,"A sẽn wa n yã bugum, n yeel a zakã rãmba: "" zĩnd-y, ad mam yãɑ bugum, raar bɩ m wa ne bug-vɩleng n wa kõ-yã maa m paam (ned) bugmẽ wã t'a wĩnig-m sorã."
  20,11,"La a sẽn wa n ta-a wã, b bool-a lame: ""Yaa fo a Muusa!"""
  20,12,"Ad yaa Maam la fo Soabã, pidg f neood a yiibã, bala fo bee Tuuwaa ko-so-yɩlengẽ wã."
  20,13,"Lɑ M tũusa foom, bɩ f kelg wahɩ M sẽn na n tʋms tɩ wa fo nengẽ wã."
  20,14,"Ad yaa Maam la Wẽnde, Soab ka be, rẽnda Maam, bɩ f tũ Maam la f yãnes Pʋʋsgã n tẽeg Mɑm yʋʋrã."
  20,15,"Ad dũni yikr yaa sẽn wa n sa, M pẽnegame n solgd-a, sẽn na yɩl tɩ b rol yõor fãa a sẽn tʋme."
  20,16,"Bɩ f ra bas tɩ ned ning sẽn pɑ kõ-a sɩdã la a pʋgd a yõorã yamleoogã wa gɩdg foom n yi-a ye, tɩ f wɑt n halkɑme."
  20,17,"La yaa bõe n be fo nug rɩtgẽ wã, yaa foo ɑ Musa?"
  20,18,"T'ɑ yeele:"" yaa m ra-saarã; m tar-a lame n tikdẽ la m tar-a n gũud m rũmsã la m leb n tar tʋlsem ɑ tɑɑb ne-a""."
  20,19,"Tɩ [Wẽnd] yeele:"" lobg-a, yaa foo Muusa""."
  20,20,"La a sẽn lobg-a wã, a lebga waɑf n zoetẽ."
  20,21,"La Wẽnd yeel yã: ""rɩk-a la f ra yaees ye, D na n lebs-a-la wɑ ɑ sẽn dɑ yɑɑ to-to wã""."
  20,22,"La rɩk f nugã n ning f kɩrengã, t'ɑ na n yiime n yɑɑ pεεlg tɩ pa sẽer ye, rẽ me yaa yel-solemd ɑ to."
  20,23,"Sẽn na yɩl tɩ Tõnd wĩnig foom D yel-solem bεdã sãndɑ."
  20,24,"Kẽng a Fɩr-aoon nengẽ, tɩ ɑd a kedgame."
  20,25,"T'a [Muusa] yeele:"" m Soabɑ! yalg m yãoogã n kõ-mɑ,"
  20,26,"La F yols m yellã."
  20,27,"La F yidg loεεgã sẽn be mam zelemdẽ wã,"
  20,28,"Tɩ b fahem mam koεεga."
  20,29,"La maan sõangd n kõ-m sẽn yi mam zakẽ wã,"
  20,30,"A Haarʋʋn sẽn yaa mam ma-biigã."
  20,31,"Keng m poorã ne-a."
  20,32,"La F lagem-a m Tẽn-tʋʋmdã pʋgẽ."
  20,33,"Sẽn na yɩl tɩ d paam n pẽgd Foom wʋsg-wʋsgo."
  20,34,"La d tẽegd F yʋʋrã wʋsgo."
  20,35,"Ad Fo yaa net ne tõndo, tõnd yellã pɑ solg Foo ye."
  20,36,"T'A yeele: "" fo sẽn kos bũmb ningã b kõ-f lame, yaa foo ɑ Muusa."
  20,37,"Ad Mam maana foom neema noor a to yεsa."
  20,38,"Wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wa n nig fo ma wã yɑmẽ wã, bũmb ning A sẽn leems-ɑ wã."
  20,39,"""T'ɑ ning-a koglgã pʋga; rẽ poorẽ bɩ f lobg koglgã kʋlgẽ wã tɩ kʋlgã na n lob-ɑ-lɑ kɩrenga, tɩ Mam bε sẽn leb n yaa ɑ bε n na n rɩk-a "". Lɑ M lob-f nonglem sẽn yi Mam nengẽ tɩ nebã nong-fo; lɑ sẽn na yɩl tɩ b wub foom Mam gũusg lɑ M gũub pʋgẽ."
  20,40,"Wɑkɑt ning fo tãoã sẽn wa n kẽnd n pʋgd n tɩ yeele: ""m wĩnig-y ned ning sẽn na n wub-a?"" Yɩɩ woto tɩ Tõnd lebs foom f ma wã nengẽ, bʋl yĩng t'a nifã mɑɑge la a ra wa sãam ɑ sũur ye. Lɑ fo sẽn wa n kʋ nedã, tɩ Tõnd tɩlg foom n yi yõkrã, la D zarb foom zarbg tεka, tɩ fo zĩnd yʋʋm saar Madyan nebã nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ tɩ fo lebg n wa B sẽn dɑ pʋlem wɑkɑt ningã; Yaa foom a Musa."
  20,41,"La M tũus foom tɩ f yɑɑ M Tẽn-tʋʋmã."
  20,42,"Kẽnge, foom ne f ma-biigã ne Mam tagmas-rãmbã la y ra wa mɑɑn yɑɑms ne Mam Yʋʋrã tẽegr ye."
  20,43,"Yãmb y yiibã, Kẽng-y a Fɩr-aoon nengẽ, tɩ ad a zʋʋgɑ toɑdgɑ."
  20,44,"Bɩ y gom ne-a koεεg sẽn bʋgse, raar ning a na tẽeg n zoe Wẽnde."
  20,45,"La b yiibã yeel yã: "" Tõnd Soaba, ɑd tõnd yaeesdame t'a nɑ n wa yãgɑ ne tõnd namsg maa a maan n zʋʋg tõnd sɩbgrã pʋgẽ."
  20,46,"T'A yeele:"" ra yaees-y ye, Mam bee ne yãmbɑ, M wʋmdame la M neẽ,"
  20,47,"Bɩ y kẽng a nengẽ n tɩ yeel-a: "" ad tõnd yaa fo Soabã Tẽn-tʋʋmb a yiibu, bɩ f yiis ɭsra'εεl koambã tɩ b tũ tõnd la f ra nams-b ye, ad tõnd waa fo nengẽ ne fo Soabã tagmas-rãmbɑ, lɑ tɩlgr be ne ned ning sẽn tũ kãndgrã!"
  20,48,"Ad B tʋma wahɩ tɩ wa tõnd nengẽ tɩ namsgã bee ne ned ning sẽn yags-a la a gũd a kudga""."
  20,49,"T'a (Fɩr-aoon) yeele: ""yaa ãnd la yãmb y yiibã Soabã, Muusa?"
  20,50,"T'a yeele: ""Tõnd Soabã la sẽn naan-a bũmbã fãa gilli, rẽ poorẽ t'A togl-ɑ."
  20,51,"T'ɑ Fɩr-aoon yeele; "" la zãma rãmb nins sẽn da reng taoorã ne kɩflmã yell yaa wãn-wãna?"""
  20,52,"La a Muusa yeel yã: ""bãmb yellã minim bee mam Soabã nengẽ, gaf pʋga, mam Soabã pa menemde, a pa yĩmdi,"
  20,53,"Ning sẽn maan-a tẽngã n kõ yãmb t'a yɑɑ sẽn sɑkd vɩɩm, la A tuk soay n kõ yãmb a pʋgẽ, la A sik sa-koom n yi saasẽ wã, n buls ne-a bõn-bundi kõbse, sẽn yaa tɩɩs toor-toore."
  20,54,"""Rɩ-y la y gũ y rũmsã, ad woto yaa tagmas ne yam-bεεl rãmba,"
  20,55,"(Tẽn-gãngã) zug la D naan yãmba, la yaa be la D na n lebs yãmba, leb n yaa beenẽ la D na n yik yãmb yik-zẽng yεsa."
  20,56,"Lɑ ad Tõnd wĩnig-a lame D tagmasã t'a yags la a tõdge."
  20,57,"N yeele:"" Fo waa tõnd nengẽ n na n yiis tõnd d tẽngẽ wã ne f tɩɩmã bɩ? Yaa foom a Muusa!"
  20,58,"Ad d na n waa ne tɩɩm woto bilgr fo nengẽ, bɩ f yãk sεk tõnd ne foo sʋkɑ; tõnd pɑ viigd-ɑ fo me ka viigd-a, la yɩ zĩig sẽn yɑɑ tẽng-n-sʋk ne d fãɑ."
  20,59,"T'a Muusa yeele:""sεkã raar na n yɩɩ tigrã raarã, wakat ning nebã sẽn wɑt n tigim sõor wakato."
  20,60,"T'a Fɩr-aoon na n gũd a kuidg n tɩ tigim a rabrã, rẽ poorẽ n na n lebg n wa."
  20,61,"La a Muusa yeel-ba: ""wɩɩbd be ne yãmba! Ra wãag-y zĩri n rogl Wẽnd t'A namsgã wa paam yãmb ye, ad ned ning sẽn wãag-a zĩri (n rolg Wẽnd) bõname""."
  20,62,"Tɩ b maan tak-n-taar bãmb ne taab sʋk b yellã zugu, lɑ b solg b yẽsgã."
  20,63,"La b yeel yã: ""ad bãmbã b yiibã yaa tɩɩm rãmba, sẽn tʋll n yiis yãmb tẽngã pʋg ne b tɩɩmã, la b paam n loog ne yãmb sorã sẽn be neerã."
  20,64,"Bɩ y tigim y dabrã tɩ tɑ, rẽ poorẽ tɩ y tong taab n wa lob y sẽn tɑrã, ad ned ning sẽn tõog-a rũndã, yẽ soab n wili."
  20,65,"La b yeel yã:"" a Muusa, maa tɩ fo reng n lobg (f rasaarã) maa tõnd yɩ pipi n lobge."
  20,66,"T'ɑ yeele: "" ɑyo, yãmb reng n lobe. La b wĩyã la b rasayã sẽn rãmbde b tɩɩmã keelem t'ɑ Muusɑ tẽed tɩ yaa wiis sẽn zote."
  20,67,"Tɩ yaeesg paam a Musa t'a solg-ɑ ɑ nengẽ."
  20,68,"Tɩ Tõnd yeele:"" ra yɑees ye, ad yaa foom n na n wili."
  20,69,"Lob bũmb ning sẽn be fo rɩtgẽ wã, a na n vela b sẽn maan yεl ninsã fãa, ad b sẽn maan bũmb ningã yaa tɩɩm raba, la tɩɩm soab me pa pɑɑmd ɑ tʋlsem a sẽn kẽng zĩig ning fãa."
  20,70,"Tɩ tɩtã-rãmb lʋɩ n maan suguudu, n yeele:"" tõnd kõo sɩd ne a Haarʋʋn la a Muusa Soabã""."
  20,71,"La a Fɩr-aoon yeel yã;"" y kõ-a-la sɩda taoor tɩ m na n ka kõ yãmb sore, ad yaa yẽ la yãmb tɑoor soɑb sẽn zãms yãmb tɩɩmã, m na n kʋʋsa y nusã la y naoã n yõs taaba, la m na n sẽb-y lame Tɑmɑr-tɩɩsã yẽgẽ, lɑ y na bãng tõnd d yiibã sʋka ãnd n yɩɩd ne namsg keelem lɑ pɑɑbo."
  20,72,"Tɩ b yeele:"" tõnd ka na n tol n sak tɩ fo n são tɑgmɑs-rãmbã nins sẽn yɑɑ vẽenes n wa tõnd nengẽ wã ye, la Soab ning sẽn naan-a tõndã me ye, bɩ f maan fo sẽn na n maan tõnd ɑ soɑbɑ, ad fo tõogã yaa dũni-kãngã vɩɩmã pʋgẽ bala."
  20,73,"Ad tõnd kõo sɩd ne tõnd Soabã sẽn na yɩl t'A yaaf d tʋʋm-tuutsã la fo sẽn modg tõnd tɩ d maan tɩɩmã, Wẽnd n yɩɩd ne sõmblem la a yɩɩd ne paabo."
  20,74,"Ad ned ning sẽn wa n wa a Soabã nengẽ n tʋm tʋʋm-wẽnse, Gεhannem be ne-a, a pa kiid a pʋgẽ, a pa vɩ me."
  20,75,"la ned ning sẽn wa A nengẽ n kõ sɩd la a tʋm tʋʋm sõma, ad bãmb rãmb tara ziir sẽn zẽke."
  20,76,"Arzãnã pʋgẽ, tɩ ko-sood zoet b tẽngrã, n na n duumd beenẽ, woto yaa ned ning sẽn yɩlg-a a meng rolbo."
  20,77,"Ad Mam tʋma wahɩ tɩ kẽng a Muusa nengẽ:"" yi ne M yemsã n pãrg sor n kõ-ba, mogrã pʋga tɩ lebg koεεnga, ra yaees tɩ b nɑ n pɑɑm-f lɑme ye, leb n da yɑees bõrbo."
  20,78,"T'a Fɩr-aoon na n pʋg-b ne a tãppã, tɩ mogrã na n bõr-b bõrb tεka."
  20,79,"Lɑ ɑ Fɩr-aoon menesa a nebã, n ka kãndg ye."
  20,80,"Yãmb ɑ ɭsraεl koambã, ad Tõnd tɩlga yãmb n yi y bε wã, la D rɩk pʋleng ne yãmb tãngã rɩtg wεεngẽ, la D sigs luiili nemd la sɩɩd-koom n kõ yãmba."
  20,81,"Rɩ-y rɩ-yɩlems D sẽn pʋɩ n kõ yãmbã la y ra wa kedg a pʋgẽ ye, tɩ Mam gẽegã wa sig y zug ye, ad Mam gẽegã sẽn wa n sig a soab zugu, a halkame."
  20,82,"La ad Mam yaa yaafg soab ne ned ning sẽn tuub-a la a kõ sɩda, la a maan tʋʋm-sõma, rẽ poorẽ t'a kãnde."
  20,83,"""La bõe yĩng tɩ fo yãg n bas fo nebã? Yaa foom a Muusa!"""
  20,84,"A yeelame:"" b bee mam poorẽ n pʋgda, la mam yãg n waa Fo nengẽ sẽn na yɩl tɩ Fo yar-mɑ""."
  20,85,"La Wẽnd yeel yã: ""ad Tõnd zarba fo nebã fo loogr poorẽ, t'a Saamiriy menes-ba."
  20,86,"T'a Muusa na n lebg n kẽng a nebã nengẽ, ne gẽeg la sũ-sãamse, n yeele:"" yaa yãmb mam nebã, rẽ yĩnga yãmb Soabã pa pʋlem yãmb pʋlen-sɩda, rẽ yĩnga yaa pʋlengã n wogl bɩ y ratame tɩ gẽeg sẽn yi y Soabã nengẽ wa paam-yã, y sẽn bas pʋlengã y sẽn dɩk ne maamã yĩnga? """
  20,87,"La b yeel yã: "" tõnd pa bas fo pʋlengã pʋgb ne tõnd tõog ye, la ad b tʋka tõnd zɩɩb sẽn yɑɑ ɑ Fɩr-ɑoon nebã nɑg-teedo tɩ d kong n lob-ɑ bokẽ wã, yaa woto la a Saamiriyy me lob (a rẽndã)."
  20,88,"N yiis nag-bil ne yĩng sẽn maand bʋʋre tɩ vɩɩm kɑ be ye, la b yeele: ""ad yaa wãnde la yãmb Soabã, a Muusa me Soabã la woto, la a yĩmame""."
  20,89,"Lɑ rẽ yĩnga yãmb pa ne t'a pa lebsd koεεg n tʋgd-ba, a leb n pa so b nang la b nafa?"
  20,90,"La ad a Harʋʋn rag n yeel-b lame sẽn reng taoore:""yaa m nebã! ad b zarba yãmb ne-a; la ad yãmb Soabã la a Yolsg Naaba, pʋg-y maam la y sak mam saglsã""."
  20,91,"B yeelame: ""tõnd ka na n bak n bas a tũub hal t'a Muusa wa lebg n wa tõnd nengẽ""."
  20,92,"A (Muusa) yeelame:"" yaa foo a Harʋʋna! bõe n gɩdg foom, f sẽn wa n yãnd tɩ b menmɑme wã,"
  20,93,"Tɩ fo bɑs-bɑ lɑ f pʋgẽ maam? Fo tõdga mam sagellã la?"""
  20,94,"A (Harʋʋn) yeelame: "" yaa m ma-biiga, ra gãd m toεεngã ye, ra gãd m zugã me ye, ad mam yaeegame tɩ f wa yeele: ""fo welga ɭsra'ɩɩl koambã ne taaba, f ka gũus mam sagls ye""."
  20,95,"T'a (Muusa) yeele:"" fo halhaal yaa wãna? foom a Saamiriy!"
  20,96,"A (Saamiriy) yeelame: ""mam yãnda bũmb ning b sẽn pa yã, tɩ m yãk tom sẽn yi Tʋntʋʋmã vũunẽ n lobe, woto la mam yõorã sagl maam""."
  20,97,"T'a (Muusa) yeele:"" kẽng n zãag maam, ad bee ne foom vɩɩmã pʋgẽ tɩ fo sã n wa yã ned bɩ fo yeel-a: "" ra sɩɩs maam tɩ mɑm pɑ sɩɩsd-f ye, (ɑ nɑ n vɩɩmsɑ wilingɑ)!"" la ad fo tara pʋleng sẽn ka na n viigi, ges fo soab ning fo sẽn da tãag n tũudẽ wã, tõnd na n yõog-a-la ne bugum, rẽ poorẽ tõnd na n sãeeg-a lame sãeegr tɛkẽ."
  20,98,"Ad yãmb Soabã yaa Wẽnd ning soab-zẽng sẽn pa be tɩ pa Yẽ wã, A minmã gũbga bũmbã fãa."
  20,99,"Yaa woto la D togsd foom kɩbay sẽn looge, la ad Tõnd kõo foom Tẽegr sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ (Kʋrãana)."
  20,100,"Ned ning sẽn gũd-a a zãn-kuidg n bas-a (Kʋrãanã), yikrã raare a na n tʋka zɩɩbo."
  20,101,"A na n duuma beenẽ, ad a sẽn tʋk yɩ wẽng yikrã raarã."
  20,102,"Raar ning b sẽn na n fʋʋs baorgẽ wã, tɩ D tigim nin-wẽnsã tɩ b nensã sobg ( yɑeesg keelem)!"
  20,103,"N walemd bãmb ne taab sʋka:"" ad yãmb sẽn zĩnd (dũni wã) yaa rasem piig bala!"
  20,104,"Tõnd n yɩɩd minim ne b sẽn yet bũmb ningã, b ned ning sẽn yɩɩd-a ne bãngr yetame: "" ad yãmb pa zĩnd (dũni wã) rẽnda raar a yembr bala""."
  20,105,"La b sokda foom tãensã yelle; yeele: ""m Soabã na n sãeeg-b lame sãeegr tɛkẽ."
  20,106,"N bas-b tɩ b legb saalle."
  20,107,"Fo pa ne golengo, fo pa ne pusbu."
  20,108,"Ra-kãng raarã b na n pʋga boaandã, gõdgr ka be ye, tɩ koeesã fãa yõgen n tees yolsg Naabã nengẽ, fo pa wʋmd bũmb ralla wɑlengo."
  20,109,"Raarã, sugsg pa nafd ralla yolsg Naabã sẽn kõ-a soab sore, n yardẽ t'a gome."
  20,110,"A (Wẽnd) mii sẽn loog bãmb taoore, la sẽn na wat b poorẽ; la bãmb minim ka gũbg Wẽnd ye."
  20,111,"Tɩ nensã yõgen n tʋg Vɩtã sẽn yaa Sek-m-meng Soabã, la ad ned ning sẽn tʋk wẽgb soab bõn yã."
  20,112,"La ned ning sẽn wa n tʋm tʋʋm-sõma, n ya sɩd-kõta, a pa na n yaees wẽgbo, a pa na n le yaees tɩ b na n wa boog a yel-sõmd ye."
  20,113,"Lɑ yaa woto la M sik Kʋrãanã ne laarabiimdu, la M yɩlem a pʋgẽ pʋlen-wẽnse, tɩ raar ningɑ b na yaees (Wẽnde), ma a kɩt tɩ b tẽeg-tẽeg taaba."
  20,114,"Wẽnd naam zẽk yã, sẽn yaa sɩd naaba, ra yãg ne Kʋrãanã karengo n lɑgmd ɑ Gibriil taoor tɩ wahɩ wã nan pa sε ye, la yeele: "" m Soaba! Paas maam bãngre!"""
  20,115,"Ad Tõnd ra rɩka pʋleng pĩnd n tʋg a Adam nengẽ, t'a yĩmi, la D pa mik loeeg ne sugr a nengẽ ye."
  20,116,"Tõnd sẽn wa n yeel Malεk-rãmbã: ""maan-y a Adam suguudu"", tɩ b maan suguudã rall a ɭblɩɩs sẽn tõdge."
  20,117,"Tɩ Tõnd yeele:"" yaa foo Adama! ad wãnde yaa fo bε, yaa fo pagã me bε, gũus-y t'a ra wa yiis yãmb arzãnã pʋg ye, tɩ yaams wa paam foom ye""."
  20,118,"Ad kom ka na n yõk foom (arzãnã pʋgẽ) ye, f ka na n kẽn zaal me ye."
  20,119,"Ko-yũud ka na n paam foom a pʋgẽ, wĩnto-sul me pa na n paam foom ye."
  20,120,"T'a Sʋtãan na n yubs-b n yeele:"" yaa foo Adama! m wĩnig foom duung tɩɩg la naam sẽn pa sεte?"""
  20,121,"Tɩ b yiibã (Adam la a Hawa) na n rɩ tɩɩgã, tɩ b yiibã yãnã na n vẽneg, tɩ b na n tõs arzãnã vãt n na n pil b yãnã, yaa woto la a Adam kɩɩs a Soabã n menem."
  20,122,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ t'a Soabã tũus-a n reeg a tuubgã la a kãnd-ɑ."
  20,123,"La A yeele:"" sig-y yãmb y yiibã (Adama la a Hawa) kaanẽ, yãmb ne taab na n yɩɩ beem, la kãndgr na n yii Mam nengẽ n wa yãmb nengẽ, la ned ning sẽn tũ-a M kãndgrã, a pa na n menemme a pa na n yɩ zu-beed soab me."
  20,124,"La ned ning sẽn gũd-a zãn-kuidg ne Mam tẽegrã, vɩɩm sẽn ya weoogr be ne-a; yikr raarã b na n yik-a lame t'a ya zoanga."
  20,125,"T'a yeele: "" yaa m Soabã! bõe yĩng tɩ Fo yik maam zoanga, tɩ mam yaool n da yaa nin-soab pĩnda?"""
  20,126,"T'A yeele: yaa woto, bala Mam tagmasã waa fo nengẽ tɩ fo yĩm-ba, yaa woto la b na n yĩm foom rũnda raarã."
  20,127,"Yaa woto la D rond ned ning sẽn maan n zʋʋge la a ka kõ a Soabã tagmas-rãmbɑ sɩda, la ad yaoolem raarã nangã n yɩɩd keelem la paabo."
  20,128,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmbã pa paam kãndgr tɩ sõor wɑoog Tõnd sẽn halk neb nins sẽn reng-b bãmbã taoorã, tɩ bãmb pɩʋʋgd b zagsẽ wã? Ad woto yaa tagmas n kõ yam bεεl rãmba."
  20,129,"Lɑ sã n ka koεεg sẽn reng fo Soabã nengẽ, (sɩbgrã) rag n na yɩ tɩlae ne-ba la yɩ wakat b sẽn yãke."
  20,130,"Bi f maan sugr ne bũmb ning b sẽn yetã la f yɩlg f Soabã yʋʋrã ne pẽka, taoor tɩ wĩntoog nan pa puki, la taoor t'a nan pa lʋɩ ye. Lɑ yʋngɑ wɑkɑto bi f yɩlg f Soabã yʋʋre, la wĩndgã kɩrensã ( zɑfɑr lɑ mɑgrib), tɩ raar ning f na yare."
  20,131,"Ra wa vɩlems f nin n tees Tõnd sẽn kõ-b sẽn yaa pagb ye; ad yaa dũni tɩ-puud bala, sẽn na yɩl n zarb-b a pʋgẽ, la fo Soabã kũunã n yɩɩd sõmblem la kellgo."
  20,132,"La sagl f zakã rãmb ne pʋʋsg la f maan sugr ne-ba, Tõnd pa sokd foom rɩtl yell ye, yaa Tõnd n rɩlgd foom, la baas neerã bee ne wẽn-zoεtbã."
  20,133,"B yeelame: ""yaa bõe yĩng la a pɑ nɑ n wat ne tõnd nengẽ yel-solemd sẽn yi a Soabã nengẽ wala sẽn be rãeenem gaf-rãmbã pʋgẽ wã?"""
  20,134,"La Tõnd sã n da halk-b-lame taoor (t'a Mohammad) nan pa wa, b rag n na n yeelame (yaoolem raarã): ""yaa d Soaba! Fo sã n dag n tʋms tõnd nengẽ tẽn-tʋʋma, tɩ d ra paam n tũ Fo Aaya-rãmbã, sẽn na yɩl tɩ d ra paam yãnd la paoor ye""."
  20,135,"Yeele: ""ad nebã fãa kolldame, bɩ yãmb me kolle! Y na wa n bãng ned ning sẽn be so-tɩrg zugu, la ned ning sẽn kãnd-a""."
